{"repo": "rmax/scrapy-redis", "pull_number": 309, "instance_id": "rmax__scrapy-redis-309", "issue_numbers": [308], "base_commit": "c3064c2fa74e623bf14448d82cc07ca2da8e183d", "patch": "diff --git a/src/scrapy_redis/scheduler.py b/src/scrapy_redis/scheduler.py\nindex ba50a10..fe3b547 100644\n--- a/src/scrapy_redis/scheduler.py\n+++ b/src/scrapy_redis/scheduler.py\n@@ -167,7 +167,7 @@ def enqueue_request(self, request):\n             self.df.log(request, self.spider)\n             return False\n         if self.stats:\n-            self.stats.inc_value(\"scheduler/enqueued/redis\", spider=self.spider)\n+            self.stats.inc_value(\"scheduler/enqueued/redis\")\n         self.queue.push(request)\n         return True\n \n@@ -175,7 +175,7 @@ def next_request(self):\n         block_pop_timeout = self.idle_before_close\n         request = self.queue.pop(block_pop_timeout)\n         if request and self.stats:\n-            self.stats.inc_value(\"scheduler/dequeued/redis\", spider=self.spider)\n+            self.stats.inc_value(\"scheduler/dequeued/redis\")\n         return request\n \n     def has_pending_requests(self):\n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "ScrapyDeprecationWarning: Passing a 'spider' argument to StatsCollector.inc_value()\nI noticed the following warning today.\n```\n2026-04-07 12:31:33 [py.warnings] WARNING: .../.venv/lib/python3.14/site-packages/scrapy_redis/scheduler.py:170: ScrapyDeprecationWarning: Passing a 'spider' argument to StatsCollector.inc_value() is deprecated and the argument will be removed in a future Scrapy version.\n  self.stats.inc_value(\"scheduler/enqueued/redis\", spider=self.spider)\n\n2026-04-07 12:31:34 [py.warnings] WARNING: .../.venv/lib/python3.14/site-packages/scrapy_redis/scheduler.py:178: ScrapyDeprecationWarning: Passing a 'spider' argument to StatsCollector.inc_value() is deprecated and the argument will be removed in a future Scrapy version.\n  self.stats.inc_value(\"scheduler/dequeued/redis\", spider=self.spider)\n```\n\nMy library version\n```\nPackage            Version\n------------------ -----------\nscrapy             2.14.2\nscrapy-redis       0.9.1\n```\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/rmax/scrapy-redis/commit/3f51f5d02a47b2971950d95f2d32f3555c09534d", "https://github.com/rmax/scrapy-redis/commit/9840c188f68572db41c34bcc5c271c63a47901d3"], "created_at": "2026-04-07T20:27:14Z"}
